	you’ve found it. Experience the perfect blend of productivity and communit
	y at Birch Road Clubhouse. We open at 8 AM every day of the year with comp
	limentary coffee\, lightning-fast Wi-Fi\, and an instant social circle wai
	ting for you. \n\nCome see if we’re your perfect fit. Join us for an Open 
	Co-working Day at your local Birch Road Clubhouse to try the club out for 
